title: AlcorMP AU6981 - AU6982 - AU6983 and more
description:

AU6981-6982-6983 v6.21 [20071227]

And also this ones is included:

SO NO GUARRANTEE FOR ANYTHING OK ? 

Anyway one worked for me in the end, took a week to find it. =P

And yes everything is rared, but there is NO password etc..
